{"tid":2444763,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是好靚午 醬麴紅燒鍋肉 配 椒鹽炸溪蝦 醃漬小菜","createTime":"2021-03-13T05:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T08:41:14.000Z","uid":33359,"like":68,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f48883b994e778df7894f348ae2df4e11394b689","tid":2444763,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99FXj5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99FXj5K.jpg&h=1b650905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bv17Hi3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBv17Hi3.jpg&h=174a241c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0NVRco.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0NVRco.jpg&h=3ae6d98f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PStxTqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPStxTqJ.jpg&h=4a220246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYaPVD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYaPVD3.jpg&h=0e55f4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個日經過見到有新開一間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就諗住今日去試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環境唔錯,夠光猛,又唔迫,坐得好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n員工服務態度都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女員工有D似台妹既嗲聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢所有餐都有包3種小菜+水果+野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n椒鹽炸溪蝦無我係烏來食既咁大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但味道都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />椒鹽味好正宗,炸得好脆,蝦味夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋呢樣野應該都唔平,因為我係烏來食細細兜都已經要100台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有醃漬牛蒡,梅乾,秋葵都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n菜上面仲淋咗少少滷肉汁,很香很好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住到主菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炸強熟咗少少,強黃可以再流質D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍋肉醬香味好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔係行滷到化哂既路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥膏位QQ地,瘦肉位彈牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫咗杯烏龍奶茶,茶味夠,但偏甜少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個袋底好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW,觀塘有唔少既台菜餐廳,但行呢種精緻路線既比較少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2b07132500ebe906fd42ce8267afc67299e2e7","tid":2444763,"uid":312130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fd58f5582f7da282fe1e7afd11d524a94b543d","tid":2444763,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"是狗飯師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcb253e3f9b33e26ec0fd127741161c90533231","tid":2444763,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da2b07132500ebe906fd42ce8267afc67299e2e7","tid":2444763,"uid":312130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b37276771bd51521fe81ff83535a23eabb79775","tid":2444763,"uid":312130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s